# Chanakya Guide (Phase 1) — Enterprise Guide Repository

Chanakya Guide is the built-in Enterprise Guide of Catalyst One.

## Knowledge SSOT

Guidance is **configuration-driven**. The Enterprise Guide Repository is the knowledge source.

- Repository: `src/constants/chanakya-guide/guidance-repository.ts` (`CHANAKYA_GUIDE_REPOSITORY`)
- Types: `src/types/chanakya-guide.ts` (`ChanakyaGuideEntry`)
- Resolve: `src/lib/chanakya-guide/`
- UI: `src/components/catalyst-one/chanakya-guide/` — **render only**, never invent mentor copy

### Entry schema (required fields)

Platform · Workspace · Section · Guidance Title · Mentor Message · Detailed Guidance · Best Practice · Recommended Next Step

Optional: Related Workflow · Related Registry · Related Enterprise Engine

## Phase boundary

Do **not** implement Success Coach, tolerance policies, resolution tasks, learning, supervisor collaboration, or coaching intelligence in Phase 1.

This repository is the foundation for Phase 2 Enterprise Success Coach.

## Certification

Every Enterprise Workspace must have Guide Repository content before it is Enterprise Certified.

If Chanakya cannot explain a page, the page is not complete — add repository entries, do not hardcode text in components.

